Description: Real Estate Opportunity Zone Fund
Full Description: The St. George Opportunity Zone Fund was created in November of 2019 with a focus on delivering substantial improvements to the St. George, Utah area.   We are offering interests in our Fund in order to raise funds to acquire, remodel, develop, lease and/or sell a number of properties located in the St. George, Utah qualified opportunity zone (“QOZ”). The St. George QOZ offers a unique opportunity to invest in properties located in downtown St. George and in its historic district. The area offers great potential for growth and value-added projects, as noted in several market study reports, highlighted below: “St. George is the fastest-growing metropolitan area in the U.S., according to new estimates from the Census Bureau. There were an estimated 165,662 people in 2017 in the designated metro area, which includes most of Washington County in southwestern Utah, up 4% from 2016, according to estimates released Thursday” Source: USA Today March 22, 2018.  The explosive growth in the greater St. George region has led to shortages of supply in both the residential and commercial markets. Commercial office rents have doubled over the past two years in several downtown commercial developments.  The Fund closed three buildings in the historic and arts district, Ancestor Square in December 2019. The property contains approximately 21,000 square feet of rentable space and is partially leased with rent escalation clauses and is currently cash-flowing. The Fund is working on substantially improving the Ancestor Square buildings as required under the QOZ legislation. The buildings are in need renovation to take advantage of their location, the appealing demographics, and the market’s continued recovery and accelerating growth.

Industry Groups: Financial Services, Lending and Investments, Real Estate

Description: SaaS to Support Your Career and Compensation
Full Description: At Earner, our mission is to right the imbalance of power between professionals and the businesses they work for.  Fundamentally, we believe too many people aren't being paid what they're worth.  It happens for a lot of reasons, but we believe with verified data and and the right support, we can get you the compensation you deserve. Earner helps you get paid fairly. First, we provide a free OfferScore, which is an evaluation of your offer letter (or letters) so you know how the offer measures up.  Most people focus on base and bonus when they look at their offers, but these only make up 70% of your total compensation. We thoroughly assess your PTO policies, 401K retirement plans, health benefits, commuter stipends, and many more to find the true value of your offer.  We build our free OfferScore by comparing your offers to thousands of others from companies like Google, Amazon, Microsoft, Facebook, Oracle, and privately-held startups - then use that data to help you negotiate effectively for a better compensation package. With an OfferScore in hand, we then work with you to build a Gameplan - that's what we call our partnering approach to negotiation.  For a flat fee, we work with you throughout the negotiation process to help you get what you deserve.  The Gameplan lays out an overall approach and specific guidance for every aspect of your negotiation, including likely counter-arguments.  We update the Gameplan as we work with you, so you always have our best advice and the right language to make your case.  If our work together doesn't result in an improved offer, you pay nothing - that's our commitment to seeing you succeed. Earner's mission is to make every professional feel valued and fulfilled by their work, and that can't happen if you're not being paid fairly.  Join us, work with us, support us in this goal!
Headquarters Regions: Greater Seattle Area, West Coast, Western US

Never before has there been a platform created solely for the glass and mirror industry. If you sell glass or mirror products and you are ready to expand beyond your existing clients to a nationwide customer base, then Glass Genius is the place for you! How it works could not be easier. First, you fill out a simple registration to create your account.
